<!-- ============================================================================
     InDows module: computer-name
     Sets the PC name automatically. Without this module Windows assigns a random
     name (e.g. DESKTOP-AB12CD3) which you can change later in Settings.

     WHERE: settings pass="specialize" > component "Microsoft-Windows-Shell-Setup"
     ANCHOR (a comment in the base) named:   [InDows:module] specialize-shell-setup

     REPLACE: __COMPUTERNAME__
       - max 15 characters
       - letters, digits and hyphens only (no spaces, no dots)
       - must not be all-numeric
       - use a single "*" to let Windows generate a random name explicitly
     ============================================================================ -->
<ComputerName>__COMPUTERNAME__</ComputerName>
